Is there any software/hardware  available which will encrypt data using
block-chaining with public key cryptography?  How slow is it compared
to DES when using RSA or the NIST algorithm?  I am not talking about
key management but about encrypting entire documents and using the
last block as a signature instead of first computing a message digest.
